The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

NATION BRIEFS

 Salem, June 12 (PTI): A 14-year-old was killed when his classmate banged his head against a wall for refusing to lend a pen. Mahendran, a Class IX student at Government Higher Secondary School in Puduchampalli, was pronounced brought dead at hospital. Vinod has been handed over to police. 

 New Delhi (PTI): Three persons have been arrested on the charge of raping a teenager in Hauz Khas in south Delhi. They were arrested after the 17-year-old domestic help told police about the incident on Monday. 




